                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def3-1137-18571026 t18571026-1137-punishment-126"></join>Confined Twelve Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Baron Martin.</hi>
